column16: Carlos Correa singles on a ground ball to center fielder Jackie Bradley.
George Springer grounds into a double play, shortstop Xander Bogaerts to second baseman Josh Rutledge to first baseman Hanley Ramirez.   Jose Altuve out at 2nd.
Jose Altuve singles on a ground ball to third baseman Travis Shaw.
Khris Davis flies out softly to right fielder Mookie Betts.
Josh Reddick reaches on a fielding error by center fielder Jackie Bradley.   Coco Crisp scores.
Jed Lowrie grounds out, second baseman Brock Holt to first baseman Travis Shaw.   Coco Crisp to 2nd.
Austin Jackson called out on strikes.
Dioner Navarro grounds out, shortstop Xander Bogaerts to first baseman Hanley Ramirez.
Jerry Sands grounds out, third baseman Travis Shaw to first baseman Hanley Ramirez.
